  ('medical-tech-moex-04325', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-111-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '張先生一年前被診斷貧血，但沒有繼續追蹤。最近食慾變差，人臉消瘦。抽血檢驗結果除貧血惡化外，出現 白血球增多。周邊血液抹片如圖，很多為具有細胞漿質外突（cytoplasma projections）的怪細胞，且這些怪細 胞有BRAF基因突變。其細胞標記為CD5-/CD23-，下列何者是最有可能的診斷？', '["Chronic lymphocytic leukemia (CLL)", "Mantle cell lymphoma (MCL)", "Hairy cell leukemia (HCL)", "B prolymphocytic leukemia (B-PLL)"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:18+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9fac9e86a627", "answer_pdf_sha1": "03d22437af06", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111100", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試醫師考試分階段考試（第一階段）、牙醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試、111年專技...", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
